J. D. KECK, Harry K. Stahler, E. A. Emerson, and Lewis Emerson, Appellants, v. CALIFORNIA SPRAY-CHEMICAL CORPORATION, Appellee. No. 11634. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 3, 1948. Nat. U. Brown, Kenneth C. Hawkins, and Brown & Hawkins, all of Yakima, Wash., for appellants. Skeel, McKelvy, Henke, Evenson & Uhl-mann and W. R. McKelvy, all of Seattle, Wash., for appellee.

• Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS, and ORR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed upon the authority of Gibson v. California Spray-Chemical Corp., Wash., 188 P.2d 316.
